items.name: Dondasch
items.addedLore: The sheer bond between Adamastor and Urdar has manifested itself into a physical form due to their duress. Such power is not to be abused...

items.name: Helm Splitter
items.addedLore: One of Skien's many deadly weapons. This warhammer, despite the massive weight of the hammerhead, was able to be swung by Skien fast enough to be a blur.

items.name: Summa
items.addedLore: An auxiliary power core of the powerful TERA-4M Mining robot line. It controls the robots by giving the bearer a compulsion to break new grounds and progress further without heed.

items.name: Durum's Serenity
items.addedLore: Carried by the Durum Protector, this small necklace holds but an ounce of the vibrance and life of the Durum Isles.

items.name: Kahontsi Ohstyen
items.addedLore: Wielded by the chief of the Tromsian jungle's zombie tribes, the augmentable crystals within it focus natural elemental energies to intense levels.

items.name: Blade of Shade
items.addedLore: The fabled weapon of the titular dark Assassin, the blade's small stature hides its true powers. Shadows undulate about the hilt.

items.name: Plague Staff
items.addedLore: Carried by the Olux Plague Doctor, this simple-looking stick subtly oozes with an unidentifiable substance that is invigorating to the holder, and lethally venomous to anything else.

items.name: Panic Zealot
items.addedLore: They must know what you went through. They must suffer the same as you did.

items.name: Haros' Oar
items.addedLore: The weathered oar of Haros, the outcast ferryman of Charon's Forsaken Legion. Magical implements have been jury-rigged onto the silver pole, glowing dull out of his bony grasp.

items.name: Stave of the Legends
items.addedLore: Crafted exclusively by the Temple of the Legends' mages, this stave is honorary to Mages who best the Temple's Grand Magus.

items.name: Deadeye
items.addedLore: The weapon of the fearsome lone bandit, Rymek Luke, it is unique in that it is designed to fire small metal rounds instead of more traditional projectiles.

items.name: Binding Brace
items.addedLore: An oppressively dark aura emanates from this shackle, dampening both the will and magic potency of those that wear it.

items.name: Marius' Prison
items.addedLore: "I know the Beast may return one day...but these chains shall bind it for eternity." The inscription glows bright in the darkness.

items.name: Slider
items.addedLore: The spelling seems to have been botched.

items.name: Zero
items.addedLore: The unstable power within this bow is capable of great destruction, but seems to zero out at the most crucial moments in battle. Only the most skillful archers can wield this weapon with confidence.

items.name: default
items.addedLore: This is a rad weapon yo. Let's make the lore longer so we can test how long it can go. Hi Jumla!
